<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_454_r1l12"><expan>Lıeb<ex>er</ex></expan> Hartman / Als vvir ew vormals <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> Jacob </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_454_r1l13">Toplers <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>Burg<ex>er</ex>s</expan> vnd ſeins <expan>arme<ex>n</ex></expan> manns <expan>vveg<ex>en</ex></expan> / 
<del rend="strikethrough"> darauf </del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_454_r1l14">
<add>vnd</add> Jr vns darauf <expan>wıd<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>geſchrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> habt / daʒ Jr des </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_454_r1l16">kein hawbtman <expan>geweſ<ex>en</ex></expan> ſeit / vnd wenn das gelt gevall was </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_454_r1l17">ew <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> cʒeteil werd / das wöllet Jr Jm <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>vveg<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_454_r1l18"><expan>wıd<ex>er</ex></expan> keren / Alſo / daʒ Jr vnd die <expan>ewr<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vor vns vnd den <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_454_r1l19">ſıcher ſeit von <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> ſache <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> / <expan>Laſſe<ex>n</ex></expan> wir ew wiſſen / Seint </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_454_r1l20">Jr des nicht hawbtman <expan>geweſe<ex>n</ex></expan> ſeit / wenn dann Jr vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_454_r1l22">die <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> tut / als Jr vns <expan>geſchrıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt / So ſüllet Jr </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_454_r1l23">vnd die <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> ſıcher ſein vor vns vnd den <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> vmb die </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_454_r1l24">ſache <expan>vngeu<ex>er</ex>lich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / <expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>ſup<ex>ra</ex></expan> </ab>
